# Profile Page Styling Tokens

## Color Usage
- Banner gradient: `linear-gradient(135deg, #112B4C 0%, #1F8A70 100%)`.
- Detail cards: background #FFFFFF, border #E2E8F0, hover elevate.
- Status badge colors: Active (#27A985), Pending (#F6B73C), Suspended (#C53030).

## Typography
- Name: 32px Satoshi SemiBold, 0.02em tracking.
- Role: 18px Satoshi Medium, color #475569.
- Labels: 14px Satoshi Medium uppercase with 0.12em tracking.

## Spacing
- Banner bottom margin 96px to accommodate overlapping avatar.
- Section spacing 48px vertical, 32px between cards.

## Buttons
- Edit Profile: Secondary outline variant.
- Message: Primary gradient.

## Responsive Behavior
- On mobile, avatar reduces to 96px and centers; action buttons stack below with 12px spacing.
- Tabs convert to horizontal scroll list with sticky top.

